In December 2009 he was voted Polish Player of the Year.<ref name="proku">{{cite news | author = | url = http://www.wiadomosci24.pl/artykul/pilkarskie_oscary_rozdane_ireneusz_jelen_pilkarzem_roku_119298--1.html | title = PiÅkarskie Oscary rozdane, Ireneusz JeleÅ piÅkarzem roku | date = 15 December 2009 | work = Wiadomosci24 | accessdate = 6 January 2010}}</ref>
During the [[2009â10 Ligue 1|2009-10 season]], he helped Auxerre to finish third in the league and win a place in the [[2010â11_UEFA_Champions_League#Play-off_round|2010â11 UEFA Champions League Play-off round]]. He finished fifth in the Ligue 1 goalscoring charts with 14 goals, despite missing some matches due to injury. Auxerre lost only once (at Grenoble 0â5) with JeleÅ in the line up on February 6 2010.
JeleÅ signed a contract as a free agent with [[Lille OSC|Lille]] at the end of August, after his contract with [[AJ Auxerre|Auxerre]] expired.<ref name="lille">{{cite news | author = | url = http://sport.onet.pl/pilka-nozna/liga-francuska/ireneusz-jelen-podpisal-kontrakt-z-osc-lille,1,4834476,wiadomosc.html | title = Ireneusz JeleÅ podpisaÅ kontrakt z OSC Lille | date = 30 August 2011 | work = onet.pl | accessdate = 30 August 2011}}</ref> ==International career== [[Image:Ireneusz Jelen.jpeg|thumb|Ireneusz JeleÅ during the 2006 FIFA World Cup game against [[Costa Rica national football team|Costa Rica]]]] As of October 2011, JeleÅ has 28 [[Cap (sport)|caps]] with the [[Poland national football team|Polish national team]]. He was selected for the 23-man squad that took part in the [[2006 FIFA World Cup]] finals in Germany and played in all three of the [[2006 FIFA World Cup - Group A|Group A]] games, almost scoring with an impressive left foot shot that hit the crossbar against [[Ecuador national football team|Ecuador]] in their 2-0 defeat. His [[trademarks]] are speed and acceleration.<ref name="soccerent">{{cite news | author = | url = http://soccernet.espn.go.com/players/international?id=36594&league=fifa.world&cc=5901 | title = ESPNsoccernet â Ireneusz Jelen Profile | date = | work = [[ESPNsoccernet]] | accessdate = 14 February 2009}}</ref>
